# marimo Notebook Competition Entries

Interactive notebooks exploring research papers through [marimo](https://marimo.io), submitted to the [alphaXiv × marimo Notebook Competition](https://marimo.io/pages/events/notebook-competition).

Each notebook takes a core research contribution and brings it to life with code, visualizations, and interactive UI elements—making complex mathematical concepts intuitive and reproducible.

